data.title: FERNANDA MACIEL - ACONCAGUA
data.description: Trail runner Fernanda Maciel follows the Mountain Athletics program to prepare for her goal: to attempt the fastest female ascent of Aconcagua, the highest summit of the Americas.

data.title: The North Face Men's Venture Jacket
data.description: The North Face Men's Venture Jacket. Ready for backcountry storms or everday excursions, this waterproof, breathable hooded jacket is designed to protect you from rain, year round. The HyVent™ 2.5L soft-shell exterior is finished with a dry-touch coating that eliminates the need for a mesh lining.
